Sofia's 100-piece collection had sat unsold on Ethereum for four months — gas fees made secondary sales hurt. A friend told her to bridge to Base and try again. She relisted at 0.01 ETH each. Within 48 hours, 62 pieces sold. A collector in Seoul messaged her: 'I've been following you since 2021. Finally I could afford one.' She cried into her coffee. This is why she made art.

